Luise S. CRISTIANI, Appellant, v. FIRST FEDERAL SAVINGS AND LOAN ASSOCIATION OF SARASOTA et al., Appellees. No. 22526. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Feb. 9, 1966. Luise S. Cristiani, pro se. W. Davis Parker, James L. Ritchey, Williams, Parker, Harrison & Dietz, Sarasota, Fla., for appellees.

Before GEWIN and COLEMAN, Circuit Judges, and McRAE, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court in this case is

Affirmed.
